y: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                       </span></div><div><en-media hash="a97a2e9555d31619311f231482006c28" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="9c2adad8caf5b79f025832045c808472" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Note: Not all Protocols do both!</span></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="2bb6cd5bdeb1fc05ba172fe34891bd9e" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span></div><div><en-media hash="d4cbbda0e67f79519902d52969eca42f" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><en-media hash="814ca19082a11aa08dcc820d88cb6d45" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                </span></div><div><en-media hash="d766b452e5b513717179e1c0f0c3a202" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">What happen if the Seq. 200 gets lost?</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                </span></div><div><en-media hash="fee59323123634a721c3fc0639a61c11" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">This is the "Error Detection" part of TCP the problem.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                        </span></div><div><en-media hash="26e43ab7278972b8bc1ca88faa4d88bd" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">After the Error Recovery, the recipient will say send me the next Sequence number ( Seq.500)</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                      </span></div><div><en-media hash="11424552ff61c08fa95acc46c9b6e1a1" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">What happen when ACK  gets lost? The sender will sit and wait for forever?</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                   </span></div><div><en-media hash="e59b2fd33b07f3d927830c580f91c819" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">The sender set an ACK Timer when it send SYNC signal </span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">If the ACT Timer expires , the sender will say this" "I didn't get an ACK for those segments, you better</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">send them again." Then the recipient will retransmit all of those segments which are in question.</span></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="f3dd95ab3454fb02ee9524804042f7cc" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 23px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal; text-decoration: underline;">Windowing</span></div><div><en-media hash="f97c956f6d3d95f493e752b225377608" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                                  </span></div><div><en-media hash="2bc5763bda464576337a74eb648a45c4" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">If no Errors ( or drops of data ), the Recipient will say "since we doing good lets increase the window's size."</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span></div><div><en-media hash="55a9def80f7d73d031501ba6fe8a7b0f" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">If some Errors start coming, the Recipient will begin decreasing the windows's size:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">                               </span></div><div><en-media hash="fea058ecfba40fcc6e2c68ff890885a8" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="9966bba0d5480ffa58b326e48d73d4f7" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="583cc3c4e34d080f51ee5102946d91fc" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">   </span></div><div><en-media hash="288b369d41a49998ad74d3ddf34fed41" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 26px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal; text-decoration: underline;">UDP Protocol</span></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="cbe80e5f4a34141428eda0f4897faa11" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">UDP Header</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">     </span></div><div><en-media hash="5e1fc6585a8b86fa3992df684e01069d" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><en-media hash="5a1ff19c54f4d57659e39fbc6b290610" type="image/tiff" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div></en-note>